snippet.title: Live Coding: File Forensics with Rust (Part 2)
snippet.description:
Last night we started working on a set of applications that would assist with basic file forensics. Let's see how many more of these we can knock out tonight.
Done:
- Getting timestamp/size/permissions of a file
- Dumping file as hex
Next up:
- Looking for ASCII characters
- Looking for file signatures
- Looking for large files
- Looking for recently changed files
- Exif data
- Steganography
